                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "魔杀绝技 · 赤牛发破！"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">怒目鬼王</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/88072335/d5b0f60e30da0341b4165d1a76b3c73b_673388046599564410.png",
                "id": "talent51614",
                "key": "最恶鬼王 · 一斗轰临！！",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "最恶鬼王 · 一斗轰临！！"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方出战角色受到伤害时：</span>抵消1点伤害。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span>，耗尽时不弃置此牌。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此召唤物在场期间可触发1次：</span>我方角色受到伤害后，为荒泷一斗附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">乱神之怪力</span>。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>弃置此牌，造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素伤害</span>。<br></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2276422835159651274.png",
                "id": "talent64532",
                "key": "阿丑",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/88072335/ea059a3f7bee2dea6bcee851752339c3_3684476586607347791.png",
                "title": "阿丑"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（冰）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（水）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（火）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（雷）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/88072335/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_762378466804260818.png",
                "id": "talent22249",
                "key": "岩元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">乱神之怪力</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色进行重击时：</span>造成的伤害+1。如果<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>至少为2，则少花费1个<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">无色元素</span>。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span>（可叠加，最多叠加到3次）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">怒目鬼王</span></strong></p><p>所附属角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">普通攻击</span>造成的伤害+2，造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>变为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素伤害</span>。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合：2</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色普通攻击后：</span>为其附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">乱神之怪力</span>。（每回合1次）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">持续回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合结束阶段，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/22/59155606/3b5977f18d39185ac0bc802fa291fb5f_461506635110722218.png",
